You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Frankfurt
TO: Lyon
BY: Train
CLASS: Economy
WHEN: Next Sunday

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <one sentence>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <one sentence>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please be specific now. Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please think about it carefully. Have you told the travel agent where you are leaving from? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for FROM invalid after max attempts.
